    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Newham rapist has his sentence increased
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Ian Vacciana has had his sentence increased following an intervention by the Solicitor General, Rt Hon Michael Ellis QC MP.</p>

  </div>
</div>

